            <p align="justify">Welcome to NT Food Technical's web site, an innovative food safety and quality service provider to the food industry. We provide a high quality and cost effective service to allow food businesses to exceed their customer's expectations through innovative solutions to food safety, quality and legality. We are here to help you meet the demands of the industry, so that you can carry on and do what you do best! Our food safety, quality and legality consultants are on hand to discuss your specific requirements and deliver a bespoke solution.</p>
            <h2 class="Size12">It is our mission to: </h2>
            <p align="justify">Have an outstanding reputation for excellence in food safety, quality and legality, and to provide the best food professionals in the industry. We know that our success lies with our ability to build strong relationships with our clients and it is our key objective to be the number one outsource technical solution. We pride ourselves on being able to offer an excellent resource service and exceed our client's expectations every time! <br />
            </p>
            <p align="justify">To find out more about NT Food Technical please look through our site or feel free to <a href="contact.htm" webstripperlinkwas="contact.htm" class="main">contact us</a> to discuss your requirements with no strings attached. </p>
            <h2 class="Size12">Company Profile </h2>
            <p align="justify">NT Food Technical was established in 2002 and has offices throughout the UK. The company was formed due to the high demand for food professionals in the industry. We help our clients to manage food safety, quality and legality within their business, whilst adding value to the operation and allowing our clients to realise their goals. </p>
            <p align="justify">Our current client base employ NT Food Technical to oversee a range of technical functions from compliance audits, specification writing, label checking to full management of their quality and technical operations. We have highly qualified and experienced consultants on hand to advise your business on all issues relating to food safety, quality and legality. For more information on the services that we offer please feel free to look through our web site or if you prefer <a href="contact.htm" webstripperlinkwas="CONTACT.HTM" class="main">contact us</a> to discuss your specific requirements and see how NT Food Technical can add value to your business. <br />
